Package de.fraunhofer.iais.eis

Interface JwtPayload

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ModelClass
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DatPayload, DatRequestPayload
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DatPayloadImpl, DatRequestPayloadImpl
    public interface JwtPayload
extends ModelClass
    The payload of an JSON Web Token as a RDF class. Is used as the common parent of e.g., DatPayload and DatRequestPayload.

      • getTransportCertsSha256

        @NotEmpty
@NotEmpty java.util.List<java.lang.String> getTransportCertsSha256()
        Separate certificates for IDS identification and transport encryption opens an attack vector for relay attacks. In order to prevent these attacks, a binding of this transport certificates to the connector is required. The inclusion of SHA256 fingerprints of currently valid transport certificates, mainly into the DAT, enables the client to relate the transport layer security with the IDS interactions. More information under https://w3id.org/idsa/core/transportCertsSha256
        Returns:
        Returns the List of Strings for the property _transportCertsSha256.
